      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "371-405",
      "markText": "许多年来，天牛庙及周围几个村的人们一直传说：宁家的家运是用女人偷来的",
      "totalCount": 1800,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=783734&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=371&rangeEnd=405",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d6f320605bf576d6f394eec?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=371&rangeEnd=405"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "783734_8_371-437",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "371-437",
      "markText": "这个世界上树木花草最是豁达，人间再大的苦难也妨碍不了它们的生长节律与热情。天牛庙围墙内外的血腥味还没有散尽，洋槐花就铺天盖地地开了。",
      "totalCount": 1264,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=783734&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=371&rangeEnd=437",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d6f320605bf576d6f394eec?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=371&rangeEnd=437"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "783734_6_1989-2059",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1989-2059",
      "markText": "那天深夜回到家，他见傻挑已经睡着，枕边放着一包没有吃完的喜果子，不禁火冒三丈，朝她腮帮子上连抽数掌，揍得傻挑醒来像上了屠案的猪一样拼命哭嚎。",
      "totalCount": 1260,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=783734&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1989&rangeEnd=2059",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d6f320605bf576d6f394eec?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1989&rangeEnd=2059"
    },
    {
