      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "8611-8663",
      "markText": "银子的下身先后有五六根棍子插进去，每根棍捣动的深度均达一两尺深……广阔的血泊里，一颗太阳在簌簌地抖动……",
      "totalCount": 1140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=783734&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=8611&rangeEnd=8663",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d6f320605bf576d6f394eec?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=8611&rangeEnd=8663"
    },
    {
