      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1954-1997",
      "markText": "他让封二将裤裆里的毛薅下七根，放在一个铁碗里，在灯头上焙焦，让女人和水服下，然后就等。",
      "totalCount": 1040,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=783734&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1954&rangeEnd=1997",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d6f320605bf576d6f394eec?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1954&rangeEnd=1997"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "783734_3_8850-8930",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "8850-8930",
      "markText": "她知道，改嫁是万万不可能的。她娘家爹是读过书的，多年来就教导她遵从圣人古训，如今岂能让她做出丢人之举？费左氏想，既然这条路不能走，那么我就走正道，求个好名声吧。",
      "totalCount": 969,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=783734&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=8850&rangeEnd=8930",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d6f320605bf576d6f394eec?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=8850&rangeEnd=8930"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "783734_3_15427-15477",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "15427-15477",
